data.description: Don't miss out on this great opportunity to own this 3 bedroom 1 & 1/2 bath home. The updated Kitchen features maple cabinetry with quartz countertops and a breakfast bar. Stainless steel kitchen appliances are all included. The living room has a beautiful bow window. The spacious backyard features a deck, a hot tub, a custom fire pit and a shed for plenty of storage options. There is a 200 amp breaker box, 90% efficiency furnace, updated windows, professionally waterproofed basement with a second sump pump.
